	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Valde sollicitus fui de remittendis epistolis, quas nuper miseras, nec ulla se captandam praebuit commoda occasio, cuius beneficio istuc possem; tandem forte fortuna nudius tertius advenit <persName ref="p20172">Ioannes ab Ulmis</persName>, affinis meus, qui sancte se curaturum recepit, ut eę ad te bona fide perferantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Eo vero die <persName ref="p8371">Albertus</persName>, meus ex fratre nepos, ad patrem scripsit inter cętera: "Deducetur ad nos <placeName ref="l2100">Bipontum</placeName> sub finem mensis huius (septembris intellige) <placeName ref="l2481">Svevię</placeName> regina, quam <persName ref="p20333">Georgius Ioannes Palatinus</persName>, illustrissimi nostri <persName ref="p18935">Wolfgangi</persName> patruelis, in uxorem ducet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Inter hosce nostros et <persName ref="p8060">electorem Palatinum</persName>, religionis excepto negocio, cęteris in rebus non male convenit; viget enim adhuc de dominicę cenę administratione controversia, cuiusque supra memini, <persName ref="p20333">Georgius Iohannes</persName> eiusdem cum electore est sententiae."</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Hactenus nepos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Bene vale, colendissime <persName ref="p495">Bullingere</persName>, meque ama et Christo Iesu commenda.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">27. octobris 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">T[uus] <persName ref="p8055">A[mbrosius] Bl[aurerus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de">Ir werdt wissen, wie der <persName ref="p20597">von Gruͦnbach</persName> <placeName ref="l1030">Wirtzburg</placeName> mitt 500 pferden und 3 fendlin zuͦ fuͦß ingenommen und der bischoff die flucht in das schlosß genommen, item das hertzog <persName ref="p18716">Erich von Brunschwig Bomberg</persName> ingenomen, ouch <placeName ref="l361">Nürenberg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l18">Augspurg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l513">Ulm</placeName> etc. knecht annemmend, und sollend die Sachsischen fürsten mitt grossem volck heruß ziechen; nitt weist man, wider wen es ist.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de">Ettlich sagend, es seye wider den pfaltzgraffen churfursten von sines gloubens wegen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Clarissimo d. <persName ref="p495">Bullingero</persName> suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de"><placeName ref="l587">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
